@{c FF00A1}Frequently Asked Questions@{c}
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯

Q: Will there be a PPC version? Hopefully already in the demo :)
A: Yes, I'm planning PPC support, at least throught PPC CyberGL,but it's far in
   future now...

Q: How large screenmodes can we use?
A: Just now, only 320x240 and 640x480 are selectable, but engine support any
   resolution upto 1280x1024 (but then it's slow like hell :-)

Q: When will be demo available ?
A: Maybe this week. I'm working very hard on this.

Q: When will be full game ?
A: I hope that about 6-9 months.  Maybe it¨s long time, but this will not be only
   simple 3D shooting game like others...

Q: Why PC version ?
A: Because I'm not Santa Claus, and I need even some money from this project ;-) But
   Amiga version will be about 0,5 year before PC version.

Q: Will be there support for 030 processors ?
A: Unfortunatelly not.  This engine needs FPU, and there are used some tricks, which
   are possible only on 040/060 processors (for example, interleaving of CPU and FPU
   instructions), which makes this engine to work on such weak processors like 040
   that fast.  So, on 030+FPU it will be working, but very slow. (I didn't test it..)

Q: What about P96 ?
A: I got a lot of e-mails from owners of P96, so I decided, that I'll make support
   even for P96.